						<summary>

						<p>On a hero-stone set up in the west of the village.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">M.K. Parakēsarivarman (Parāntaka I) Year 30: 937 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the death of Maṉukulaṉ Siṅgaperumāṉ, son of Iḷakāmuṇḍaṉ of Mēlaḍaiyūr-nāḍu, in a cattle-raid after the recovery of the buffloes.</p>						

